Slovakia Won’t Demand Haircut for Greece Investors, Sme Reports

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-07-07T07:14:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/slovakia-won-t-demand-haircut-for-greece-investors-sme-reports.html
Slovak lawmakers rejected a motion
that would force Finance Minister Ivan Miklos to demand a cut in
the nominal value of  Greece ’s debt,  Sme  newspaper reported,
citing the result of the parliamentary vote.  To contact the reporter on this story:
